<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <!-- Standard Meta -->
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
  <link href="/favicon.jpg" mce_href="/favicon.jpg" rel="bookmark" type="image/x-icon" />
  <link href="/favicon.jpg" mce_href="/favicon.jpg" rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" />
  <link href="/favicon.jpg" mce_href="/favicon.jpg" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" />
  <!-- Site Properities -->
  <title>思达教育</title>

  <!--<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:400,700|Open+Sans:300italic,400,300,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>-->


  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>

  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

</head>
<body id="home">
<div class="ui inverted page grid masthead segment">
  <div class="column">
    <div class="inverted secondary pointing ui menu">
      <div class="header item">思达教育</div>
      <div class="right menu">
        <a class="item login_link">登陆</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% cat_pic= "cat#{rand(1..3)}.png" %>
    <img src="<%= asset_path cat_pic %>" class="ui medium image">

    <div class="ui transition information visible">
      <h1 class="ui inverted header">
        2015火热招生中
      </h1>

      <p>
        SAT TOEFL 精品培训
      </p>
      <h5>
        咨询电话 028-86958337
      </h5>

      <div class="large basic inverted animated fade ui button">
        <div class="visible content">了解详情</div>
        <div class="hidden content">了解详情</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="ui page grid overview segment">
  <div class="ui two wide column"></div>
  <div class="twelve wide column">
    <div class="ui three column center aligned stackable divided grid">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui icon header">
          <i class="circular book link icon"></i>
          课程
        </div>
        <p>SAT TOEFL 等课程安排</p>

        <p><a class="ui teal right labeled icon button" href="#">了解更多 <i class="right long arrow icon"></i></a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui icon header">
          <i class="circular code link icon"></i>
          讲师介绍
        </div>
        <p>来自五湖四海的精英讲师们</p>

        <p><a class="ui teal right labeled icon button" href="#">了解更多 <i class="right long arrow icon"></i></a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui icon header">
          <i class="circular user link icon"></i>
          交流
        </div>
        <p>学员的各种评价和反馈</p>

        <p><a class="ui teal right labeled icon button" href="#">了解更多 <i class="right long arrow icon"></i></a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ui inverted page grid stackable relaxed feature segment">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="column">
      <h1 class="center aligned ui header">
        英语学习技巧
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="ten wide column">
      <h2 class="ui header">托福考试备考辅导：提升10分的15个考试技巧</h2>

      <p>托福考试也需要有一些小技巧的，以下为大家分享的15个托福考试技巧，将有助你提升托福考试成绩哦，快来看看吧。
        <br>
        1.在听力完成后会有5秒倒计时，结束后开始计时10分钟的休息，休息完后让监考输入密码进入口语部分，按完第一个NEXT后别按第二个NEXT，这样中间就有无限的时间听别人答完所有的题。第1，2题也要做笔记，虽然短而且简单，但这样可以防止到时万一因为某个词而卡住。
      </p>

      <div class="ui basic inverted animated button button">
        <div class="visible content">更多</div>
        <div class="hidden content"><i class="right arrow icon"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ui inverted section divider"></div>
      <h3 class="ui header">更多文章</h3>

      <div class="ui inverted animated selection list">
        <div class="item">
          美剧超流行的10句实用口语
          <div class="right floated">Jan 20, 2014</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          美国习惯用语汇总
          <div class="right floated">Jan 1, 2014</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          英语常用口语118句
          <div class="right floated">Dec 20, 2013</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="six wide column">
      <div class="ui secondary form segment">
        <h3 class="ui header">获取每日学习小贴士</h3>

        <p>订阅邮件以便接收英语学习的小贴士，您可以随时取消订阅</p>

        <div class="field">
          <div class="ui left icon action input">
            <i class="user icon"></i>
            <input name="email" type="text" placeholder="name@email.com">

            <div class="ui teal submit button">订阅</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ui error message"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="ui inverted teal page grid segment">
  <div class="ten wide column">
    <div class="ui three column stackable grid">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui header">Courses</div>
        <div class="ui inverted link list">
          <a class="item">Registration</a>
          <a class="item">Course Calendar</a>
          <a class="item">Professors</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui header">Library</div>
        <div class="ui inverted link list">
          <a class="item">A-Z</a>
          <a class="item">Most Popular</a>
          <a class="item">Recently Changed</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui header">Community</div>
        <div class="ui inverted link list">
          <a class="item">BBS</a>
          <a class="item">Careers</a>
          <a class="item">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="six wide right floated aligned column">
    <h3 class="ui header">联系我们</h3>
    <addr>
      237 二环路东三段35号 <br>
      四川省 成都市 <br>
    </addr>
    <p>(404) 867-5309</p>
  </div>
</div>
<% unless flash[:notice].blank? %>
    <script>
      alert("<%= flash[:notice] %>");
    </script>
<% end%>

<div class="ui dimmer page hidden">
  <div class="ui test modal transition hidden" style="margin-top: -250px;">

    <i class="close icon"></i>



    <div class="content">
      <div class="ui header">用户登陆
      </div>

      <%= form_tag action="session/create",{class:"login_form"} do%>
          <div class="ui form">
            <div class="ui three fields">
              <div class="field">
                <input type="text" name="login_name" placeholder="登陆账户名">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <input class="password optional" id="user_password" name="password" type="password" placeholder="密码">
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="actions">
            <div class="ui black button">
              关闭
            </div>
            <%= submit_tag '登陆',{class:"ui positive right labeled icon button"} %>

          </div>

      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
